&lt;DIV&gt;But.... It adds value to Mages, who sorely need it. /cheer Magicians!!!&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;And restores, to a very small degree, some value to Necros that was lost with the Summonning altars.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I do not see this as game-breaking and i *do* see this as a HUGE help reducing LFG... &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Consider:&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;You get the tell inviting you to a group in Zone X. You can get the invite immediately. You can zone in and get CoH'd or use /findPC to find the camp.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
